== Spanish == 
=== Etymology ===
Quechua [[yapay]], to add, to increase
=== Noun === 
'''yapa''' ''f'' 
# Something that is added, especially something that a merchant gives to a buyer to complete the amount requested, or something [[extra]] given as a [[bonus]]; a [[gratuity]], [[lagniappe]].
